args: a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Adding the same generated offset must preserve less-or-equal ordering.
law: (if (fuzz-lte? {a} {b}) (fuzz-lte? (fuzz-add {a} {c}) (fuzz-add {b} {c})) True)
